Friends and family of late kwaito star Sbusiso “R Mashesha” Khomo of Big NUZ fame are planning to keep his legacy alive.His family, friends and the community have decided to hold an annual event to keep his memory alive.It’s been three years since his death. His sister Zonke Mbele said the family was approached by Sbusiso’s friend Bandile Kubheka, who suggested they have an annual event in his honour to motivate kids from the community. if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjss6fb2g-XCTvNEhi1X_pXnYD00OO40uYMjU74My-9AXPyCMN3I1uUgOYDU57PkyYjBbKY-xL0BbN6wI9709bH41tLdEySlL-Lzt6Svw_LCDn357XQiF6caBhNQC5UqZdUfhmz89I3nzhjvGM-rAzZ1cWV56NpB7Cw8KbpEwnOKBF19RX761sfXMRXv3E_D06RdP5ICbqMOWUTAatbmA2N0vUkJiOyJqXhfBjtGzVlcpxfEfXaid78g8uMNELpj4lGStF4-d4ifL_deA2E_YYXYvbgFDZBMchaf79Q\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzEEPQBlAWctMEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
